quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  9,69,"[Hi…ďe mba'i] wano …ďeen adinoo…ďe on : …ďe laatinoke …ďur…ďe on sa…ótude doole, …ďur…ďe on …óuu…óude jaw…óeele e …ďi…ó…ďe. ∆Āe dakmitori [ontuma] e ge…óal ma…ď…ďe ngal dakmitor…óon ge…óal mon ngal wano adinoo…ďe on …ďen dakmitornoo ge…óal ma…ď…ďe ngal, jnumpir…óon wano …ďe njumpirnoo. …ďeen …óoon, golle ma…ď…ďe …óen po…ďii(njirbii) aduna e laakara. Ko …ďeen …óoon ngoni hayru…ďe(perdu…ďe) …ďen."
  9,70,"E kabaaru …ďen adinoo…ďe …ďe araali …ďe : yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďen, e Aadi'en, e Thamuuda'en, e yim…ďe Ibraahiima …ďen, e wonndi…ďe Madyana …ďen e waylitanoo…ďe …ďen? Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen addani …ďe hujjaaji …ďanngu…ói.=pee√Ī…ói Alla wonaani too√Īoowo …ďe, ko woni tan ko woŇčkiiji ma…ď…ďe …óin …ďe wonunoo too√Īude."
  9,71,"GooŇč…óim…ďe wor…ďe …ďen e gooŇč…óin…ďe rew…ďe …ďen yoga ma…ď…ďe ko walloo…ďe yoga. Hi…ďe yamira mo∆ī∆īere, …ďe ha…óa Ňči√Īere=bone, …ďe √Īii…ďna juulde, …ďe totta zakka, …ďe …óoftoo Alla e Nualaa…óo makko on. …ďen …óoon, arma Alla yurmee …ďe. Pellet, Alla ko poolu…óo, √Ďee√Īu…óo."
  9,72,"Alla fodanii gooŇč…óin…ďe wor…ďe …ďen e goo…óin…ďe rew…ďe …ďen Aljannaaji, …ói caatli ilata e ley majji, ko …ďe duumotoo…ďe nder majji, e ko…óooli laa…ďu…ói e nder Aljanna duumal. E yarluyee=weluye Alla …ďur…óo mawnude. Ko …óum woni malal mawnungal."